narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely take it! If you want to learn the technical basics of photography and Photoshop, this class will teach you that. But even if you already know the basics, you'll still get an lot out of this class from looking at other artists and having your work critiqued.

This course will require you to work hard, but you will get out of it what you put in. Be warned that if you don't have a camera, this class could be very expensive for you. However I think this is definitely a worthwhile class to take if you are interested in photography.
